### ============================================================
### Exemplos de requisições — Ledger API
### Use com a extensão REST Client do VS Code
### ou importe no Postman/Insomnia
###
### ANTES DE USAR:
### 1. Rode o setup: .\scripts\setup-local.ps1
### 2. Gere o token: dotnet run --project tools\GenerateDevToken -- LedgerAdmin
### 3. Cole o token na variável @token abaixo
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token   = COLE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### IDs de seed (gerados pelo 003_SeedData.sql)
@accountComSaldo    = aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa
@accountSegundo     = bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb
@accountZerado      = cccccccc-cccc-cccc-cccc-cccccccccccc
@entryDebitSeed     = e3333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HEALTH CHECK (sem autenticação)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CRÉDITO DE PONTOS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Credit — Acúmulo de pontos por compra
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ledger/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-credit-001

{
  "accountId": "{{accountComSaldo}}",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "occurrenceDate": "2026-06-01T10:00:00-03:00",
  "idempotencyKey": "magalu-order-99887766",
  "statementMetadata": {
    "partnerId": "MAGALU",
    "productName": "Smart TV 55\"",
    "description": "Pontos acumulados na compra #99887766"
  }
}

###

### Credit — Replay idempotente (mesma idempotencyKey — deve retornar 200 com IsIdempotentReplay=true)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ledger/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-credit-001-replay

{
  "accountId": "{{accountComSaldo}}",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "occurrenceDate": "2026-06-01T10:00:00-03:00",
  "idempotencyKey": "magalu-order-99887766",
  "statementMetadata": {
    "partnerId": "MAGALU",
    "productName": "Smart TV 55\"",
    "description": "Pontos acumulados na compra #99887766"
  }
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DÉBITO DE PONTOS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Debit — Resgate de pontos (deve passar — saldo suficiente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ledger/debit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-debit-001

{
  "accountId": "{{accountComSaldo}}",
  "amount": 300.00,
  "occurrenceDate": "2026-06-01T11:00:00-03:00",
  "referenceId": "ORDER-ECOMMERCE-55443",
  "idempotencyKey": "livelo-resgate-55443",
  "statementMetadata": {
    "partnerId": "LIVELO",
    "productName": "Passagem Aérea GRU-GIG",
    "description": "Resgate de milhas — voo LA456"
  }
}

###

### Debit — RN01: Saldo insuficiente (deve retornar 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ledger/debit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-debit-rn01

{
  "accountId": "{{accountZerado}}",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "occurrenceDate": "2026-06-01T11:00:00-03:00",
  "referenceId": "ORDER-FAIL-001",
  "idempotencyKey": "fail-saldo-insuficiente-001",
  "statementMetadata": {
    "partnerId": "AMAZON",
    "productName": "Kindle Paperwhite",
    "description": "Tentativa de resgate com saldo zero"
  }
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ESTORNO DE PONTOS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Refund — Estorno total do débito seed (e3333333...)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ledger/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-refund-001

{
  "accountId": "{{accountComSaldo}}",
  "originalTransactionId": "{{entryDebitSeed}}",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "occurrenceDate": "2026-06-01T12:00:00-03:00",
  "reason": "Cancelamento de pedido pelo cliente",
  "idempotencyKey": "refund-order-seed-001",
  "statementMetadata": {
    "partnerId": "AMAZON",
    "productName": "Estorno — Passagem Aérea GRU-GIG",
    "description": "Cancelamento solicitado pelo cliente em 01/06/2026"
  }
}

###

### Refund — Estorno parcial
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ledger/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-refund-parcial

{
  "accountId": "{{accountComSaldo}}",
  "originalTransactionId": "{{entryDebitSeed}}",
  "amount": 200.00,
  "occurrenceDate": "2026-06-01T12:30:00-03:00",
  "reason": "Estorno parcial — item indisponível",
  "idempotencyKey": "refund-parcial-seed-001",
  "statementMetadata": {
    "partnerId": "AMAZON",
    "productName": "Estorno Parcial — Passagem GRU-GIG",
    "description": null
  }
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROS DE VALIDAÇÃO (400)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Validação — Amount zero (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ledger/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "{{accountComSaldo}}",
  "amount": 0,
  "occurrenceDate": "2026-06-01T10:00:00-03:00",
  "idempotencyKey": "key-amount-zero",
  "statementMetadata": {
    "partnerId": "MAGALU",
    "productName": "Produto X",
    "description": null
  }
}

###

### Validação — XSS injection no ProductName (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ledger/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "{{accountComSaldo}}",
  "amount": 100,
  "occurrenceDate": "2026-06-01T10:00:00-03:00",
  "idempotencyKey": "key-xss-test",
  "statementMetadata": {
    "partnerId": "MAGALU",
    "productName": "<script>alert('xss')</script>",
    "description": null
  }
}
